Relevant ScaleBuild Capabilities: Custom AI/ML models, computer vision for manufacturing and security, enterprise workflow automation, full-stack SaaS development, data pipelines

Write a LinkedIn outreach message following this EXACT structure:

1. HOOK (1-2 sentences): Reference their specific pain point or need directly. Make it personal and precise.
2. CREDENTIALS (2-3 sentences): Mention ScaleBuild AI builds custom AI/ML models, computer vision systems for manufacturing and security, and enterprise automation. Reference ex-Intel/IBM/Micron engineering background and shipped production systems.
3. SOFT CTA (1 sentence): Low-pressure ask — happy to connect or have a quick conversation if relevant.

RULES:
- 150-200 words total
- Tone: direct, confident, no fluff, human-sounding, like one founder to another
- NO em dashes
- NO exclamation marks
- Do not start with "I hope" or generic openers

Sign-off:
Ujjwal Roy
CEO, ScaleBuild AI

Return ONLY the message text. No markdown. No subject line.`
  }]
}) }}

